item.description: "TO EFFECT CHANGE BY ADVANCING COMPANIES AND PEOPLE TO THE NEXT LEVEL" The Ways We Do This: With honesty, by outreach, by being excellent at what we do, by tackling the hardest 10%, through coaching and mentoring. We go deep but we do it with a lightheartedness that makes the process fun and inviting. We cherish the opportunity to highlight good in others, defend others, and assist in the development and progress of others.
